Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.49,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.65,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.21,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.35,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:22.70,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:27.43,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:34.37,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right. It was the four of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We four planned it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought we could force you to resign,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...if we exposed the secret between you and Misonoo Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That was our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as it turned out, we couldn't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no secret to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are our resignations...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You resign? Of your own free will?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, there's one thing I hope you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This was something we did solely to protect the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorority can't be maintained solely on the strength of your pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we need something other than idealism and pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, we might try inviting some regular students to some of our parties,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...or opening up the Sorority opera concert to the student body, even!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We need some new ideas to insure that the Sorority continues to exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To insure that the Sorority continues to exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! What if the Sorority perishes because of your stubborn pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...where's the good in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to work to protect the special Sorority privileges we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Listen to you, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really all the Sorority means to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,32. Pride, and the Final Meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please lend us your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One simple vote, and the Sorority is abolished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please support us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...my newly found Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Our petition is progressing very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, we reached the one-third mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, reaching the one-half mark this week might be no fantasy after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going well, perhaps even too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My Brother, at times like this I find myself pondering things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really the right thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I be involved in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The better things go, the more I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you ever feel that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is what happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a place where we can sign too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Katorea-no-Kimi! Vampanera-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! You're all important Sorority members!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you... leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we did. Just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome. The best of luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...today I noticed something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bit by bit, the Sorority has begun to unravel from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, wait! Yamamoto-san! Hoshino-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing? How can you sign the petition?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This movement is why we were expelled from the Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you support the campaign?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no right to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to leave the Sorority because of our involvement with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But now... but now, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the future matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,After being expelled from it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...we'll not rest easy until that Sorority is abolished. Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! How can I watch Miya-sama's followers living the high life as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't watch all that from the sidelines!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to end the Sorority forever than to suffer through that. Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We could never... feel that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... well, it's like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best to just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Katorea-no-Kimi and Vampanera-no-Kimi signed, as you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:08:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then today they were joined by Mona-Lisa-no-Kimi and Borgia-no-Kimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All four of them have resigned as members.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They may do as they wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But they say the petition has been signed by nearly half the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand me that vase, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Medusa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, more than half!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When Mona-Lisa-no-Kimi and Borgia-no-Kimi signed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...it seemed to turn the tide in our favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When it reaches two-thirds, shall we present it to the school board?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hardly believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That the Sorority is so intensely hated by so many students,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's hard to believe. I don't want to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how it really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to this then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Today a classmate shoved a petition book in my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, here's what she says: "Sign it."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you do, I'll forgive you for everything you did in the past."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I had sinned merely by joining the Sorority...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it would be wiser... not to stick with the Sorority,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...because of the social backlash following the abolition of the Sorority...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! You mustn't allow yourself to get demoralized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you realize that now, of all times,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...is the time you must support Miya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heartbreaking to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You, who were once our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, here's someone who signed up to abolish the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't recall any friend who would do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why stay with the sinking ship until the very end,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...when only the captain gets any glory from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The best course... is to abandon ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right out! Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I have something I must ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can answer just with a "yes" or "no".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become part of the petition drive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do that just because you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say "yes" or "no".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I do hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No... but I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate? ...but I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I love you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I hate you! Hate you! Hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What was its name...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That tiny village had a beach... its name escapes me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There was the roar of the surf in my ears...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...and snow falling, as if it didn't know how to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember that part well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But somehow, the name still eludes my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:14:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I realized I had forgotten that one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...despite its importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite how utterly vital it is for the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me... tell me that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you couldn't have forgotten it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've forgotten... Then, I'll forget, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tea ceremony... Did you say, tea ceremony?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. A tea ceremony, after school, at the Sorority House.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All Sorority members are invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All the members?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...you are the only senior member remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relying on you to choose those who make the preparations,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...and to summon all of the members.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way... I gave official notice to the school board today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You are replacing Komabayashi-san as vice-president of the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,These are difficult times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A tea ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The remaining members are making a last stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This has become quite a crisis, hasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...a third of the Sorority have either resigned or signed the petition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time I come back to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...things might be completely different there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me that it isn't just the school...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...perhaps people's minds have changed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer to believe that it is only on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my father's old novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya-san... um... Takashi-san had a copy and gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it seems like so long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa had just met my mother. He fell in love with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...and they'd begun to live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That was before I was born, and before he was a famous writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They were so poor they couldn't even pay the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Papa's wild youth... he had only his dream then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When he had only love and talent to comfort him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...this is the novel that reflected those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a very, very beautiful novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...and though it's true that he is known as a porn writer now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...my finding that he'd written this made me so happy deep inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It filled me with pride to know that I am his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...that this was who he really was, that I'd found his true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I read it? I'd like to borrow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, me too! After Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She hopes the changes are only surface ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...so that our souls can remain forever unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that is what Mariko-san wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama, the tea ceremony is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just under two-thirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? After all that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. There's tomorrow, and the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you'd better stop doing that in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear? About the tea ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, none of the members are going...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The ex-members managed to organize a boycott.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the end of Miya-sama, then, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? You, alone, prepared all the flowers and tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... no one else... was willing to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you try one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask all the members to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll do that. Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama is waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's alone! Alone and waiting at the Sorority house!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No! The Sorority is going to be abolished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of being looked down on by my classmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Miya-sama is there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you take advantage of this opportunity too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you refuse to return to the Sorority house,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...then you can join the rest of us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Orihara-san... do you think you could convince her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her that the era of Miya-sama is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The era of Kaoru-no-Kimi is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The strongest candidate to replace Miya-sama is Kaoru-no-Kimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Katsuragi-san? It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just declare your resignation here in front of Orihara-san, and you'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen here, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I started this campaign was to put an end to that sort of thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This leads to the same rotten situation as before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama... Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long... I've kept you waiting so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, everyone is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin. Let's start, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.79,0:21:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to a Sorority House tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.15,0:22:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this Sorority House.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I love all things beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I love those things which bring dignity to us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather... I seek to perfect my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I seek to devote my love to that which brings dignity, beauty, and lasting value.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I seek to become one who loves these things well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I seek to elevate myself to that high standard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pride is something you cannot have unless you long for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.77,0:22:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I am always asking myself if I truly have such pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I do not know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,From time to time, I may feel as if I want to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know it cannot be attained without sufficient longing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So I seek constantly to grow and maintain my dignity and pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...no matter what may happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.77,0:23:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To all of you Sorority members,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.78,0:23:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...let me say that as long as I feel thus, I will continue as president of the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I am the only one... this is where I will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.51,0:23:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please enjoy your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.27,0:23:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san's father wrote something similar in his novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"If one never accepts anything less
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...than those things which are worthy of the greatest sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...then no matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.34,0:23:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,even if every drop of blood leaves your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...you will suffer no regrets."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.11,0:24:14.31,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.31,0:24:19.78,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.25,0:24:25.39,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.39,0:24:30.86,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.60,0:24:37.14,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.14,0:24:42.61,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.61,0:24:45.34,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.34,0:24:48.15,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.15,0:24:50.55,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.55,0:24:55.82,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
